Class Sort

java.lang.Object
util.Sort
public class Sort extends Object
A utility class for sorting appointments and providers. The class provides methods to sort lists of appointments and providers based on various criteria using a selection sort algorithm.

    • compareAppointments

      private static int compareAppointments(Appointment a1, Appointment a2, char key)
      A helper method that compares two appointments based on the specified key.
      Parameters:
      a1 - The first appointment to compare.
      a2 - The second appointment to compare.
      key - The key(s) to compare by.
      Returns:
      -1 if a1 is less than a2, 0 if they are equal, 1 if a1 is greater than a2.
